author: The Current
description:
To celebrate The Current’s 20th Anniversary, The Current’s Live Sessions Vault unlocks never-before-seen live performance videos of bands and artists who have played in our iconic studio. 

Watch to see the full three-song session of Phoebe Bridgers, featuring previously unreleased footage, from when she visited The Current studio back in 2018.

Songs Performed 
00:00:00 Scott Street
00:04:58 Smoke Signals
00:10:34 Motion Sickness

Musicians
Phoebe Bridgers – vocals, guitar
Anna Butterss – bass
Marshall Vore – drums, vocals
Nick White – keyboard
Harrison Whitford – guitar, vocals

Credits
Engineer – Mike DeMark, Brandon Smith
Producer – Derrick Stevens
Visuals  – Nate Ryan
Digital Producer – Natalia Toledo
Graphics – Natalia Toledo

The Current’s Live Sessions Vault is supported by the Minnesota Orchestra, GS Motors, and Delta Dental of Minnesota Foundation.
